A Petrol Bomb (molotov Cocktail ) used aginst tanks and infantry.
Known issues: could not add physics volume to deal damage in an area set on fire.
Will deal damage to Pawn standing in area set on fire only if said pawn is moving.

Can be deflected off tank if thrown under small angle
Inherited from the Panzerfaust.
Must do: do not use faust as parent.
Deal damage to any vehicle no matter of armor (no penetration check of course)
Deal extra damage if thrown on critical areas, like engine radiator and other openings.
Deal DoT.

Downsides: needs custom pawn in orded to support setting palyers on fire.
